snippet: Ryan Malone tied the score late in regulation and got the deciding goal in the ninth round of the shootout as the New York Rangers beat the Chicago Blackhawks 3-2 in a preseason game Friday night....

headline.print_headline: Malone Lifts Rangers Past Blackhawks, 3-2 in SO
headline.main: Malone Lifts Rangers Past Blackhawks, 3-2 in SO

lead_paragraph: Ryan Malone tied the score late in regulation and got the deciding goal in the ninth round of the shootout as the New York Rangers beat the Chicago Blackhawks 3-2 in a preseason game Friday night.
